data.description: Situated on top of a private hill, this updated home sits on 1 acre of land with unobstructed views. Inside, the home offers a roomy and bright open design with an expansive kitchen offering generous counter space and cabinets. The split-floor plan provides privacy to the primary suite with its en-suite bathroom. With a gas log stove in the living room and central air conditioning, you’ll enjoy tucking in the winter and relaxing in the summer heat. Covered patios and decks surround the home, giving you several places to sit back and enjoy the views. Several outbuildings grace the property providing workshop, storage, and hobby space. The property further features a dedicated RV space with new electricity and sewer. If you’re looking for something with a little room to breathe, you won’t want to miss this one.
